{"tid":584166,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片·IS童兵】4歲拿槍7歲拿刀處決囚犯　高叫：真主偉大","createTime":"2018-03-07T15:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T00:27:33.000Z","uid":56002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dccd18dd7f3bc0f62528a098cef2c726a5461da6","tid":584166,"uid":56002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"【橙訊】恐怖組織「伊斯蘭國」(ISIS)近日發佈最新宣傳影片，驚見兩名稚嫩的童兵拿著刀槍對著囚犯又掃射又割喉，並且舉槍大叫「真主偉大！」<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，影片首先顯示，一名年約7歲的孩子在廢棄公園內走向一名囚犯，並從身邊的恐怖分子手上拿起一把刀，走到囚犯面前摀住其嘴部向上仰起，露出頸部，該恐怖分子給了他「行刑」的指示，不過沒有行刑畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/232341_74e8eb02f451eb725363209e3c442d69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F232341_74e8eb02f451eb725363209e3c442d69.png&h=aec309b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/232446_e12679c2f274bc282bdbbdec23692d0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F232446_e12679c2f274bc282bdbbdec23692d0b.png&h=5572df8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片其後顯示另一名年約4歲的男童，從身邊人手上接過一把小槍，舉槍對準囚犯頭部，更大喊「真主至大！」<br />\n<br />\n影片引起不少網民反感，直言「真的沒有辦法看下去！」、「這些小孩為什麼要承受大人的戰火？」、「這年紀不該是在這樣的狀況下成長。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/232527_32a149ad4b9334637fb70815d7afa252.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F232527_32a149ad4b9334637fb70815d7afa252.png&h=46a3e985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞來源:<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/03/07/010084347.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F010084347.shtml&d=fCaBwbOXOM5hpPmwtkDIYoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=bb986326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/03/07/010084347.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"818a3c5a006eae715b85152abaa33d0620535baa","tid":584166,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T23:27:28.000Z","msg":"滅晒成個族就差唔多㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4fa489ff4582363f78244024b4aab9144d344a","tid":584166,"uid":30459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T23:44:19.000Z","msg":"教佢地睇高達囉"},{"pid":"51a3a80b1fa1ccbd4db1dfcbd32cfe1bccbab696","tid":584166,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:11:18.000Z","msg":"當兵見到細路都無得手軟"},{"pid":"45de7cadd3803ad4f65f99f441036f666bb0a4a6","tid":584166,"uid":138606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:21:41.000Z","msg":"4歲細路仔嘅手 BB彈槍嘅後座力都唔知受唔受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ccedf43cf27ae8dde93e73960e4e3c0cf73ac1","tid":584166,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:27:33.000Z","msg":"為大規模炸平isis作出準備<br />\n<br />\n唔怕左膠屌話殺錯平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}